Phaxio,lets,developers,build,faxing,capabilities,into,systems,with,a,simple,API,The,API,exposes,functionality,such,as,sending,and,receiving,faxes,Users,can,also,provision,phone,numbers,and,get,account,status,and,list,faxes,in,a,date,range,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON